Package com.flipkart.dao

Interface FlipFitAdminDAOInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
FlipFitAdminDAO
public interface FlipFitAdminDAOInterface
Interface for FlipFit Admin DAO (Data Access Object). This interface defines methods for admin-related operations such as registering admins, approving or rejecting gyms and gym owners, and viewing their approval statuses.
